{"id":335376,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/【异闻观止】伍皓-藏头记事诗：危难关头/","date":"2014-03-03T13:56:33Z","modified":"2015-03-29T09:41:09Z","title":"【异闻观止】伍皓 | 藏头记事诗：危难关头","content":"<p>@伍皓红河微语：3•01暴恐虽事发昆明，但红河作为周边，我们当晚就紧急调度支援昆明，到现在，连续两天两夜，我只囫囵了两三个小时。作为党委政府的一员，在危机中，我深感应肩负起维护民众安全之责；两天来，市民们的良知善行，更无时无刻感动着我。这几句写于彻夜应急间隙的小诗，真实地记录了两天来我的亲历亲见。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6316fcb7jw1ee2gnb8seuj20hs1w8qbm.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-335377\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6316fcb7jw1ee2gnb8seuj20hs1w8qbm.jpg\" alt=\"6316fcb7jw1ee2gnb8seuj20hs1w8qbm\" width=\"440\" height=\"1688\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6316fcb7jw1ee2gnb8seuj20hs1w8qbm.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6316fcb7jw1ee2gnb8seuj20hs1w8qbm-78x300.jpg 78w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,20505],"tags":[27447,8635,9941,24714,17915,9503]}